Exercise 3 - Data Analysis

A sample text file that holds employees data is attached with the homework. Each line has the following
data elements (separated by commas):
Name, DOB, Salary

Write a Java based code to answer the following questions:
 How many Employees exist in the file?
 Who has the highest salary?
 What is the average salary?
 How many employees make above the average?
 What is the average age of employees?

Write to an output file the employee names sorted according to their salary? (Make sure to well format
the output file)
